# 🎯 CODE VISUALIZER - CLI to GUI Revolution

**Turn AI-generated code into interactive visual tiles!**
![Code Visualizer Demo](./images/Demo.png)

![Code Visualizer Demo - Expanded](./images/Demo1.png)

![Code Visualizer Demo - Edit Dialog](./images/Demo2.png)


## 💡 The Problem
- AI generates 200+ lines of complex code
- Beginners can't understand "what does what"
- Hard to communicate specific modifications

## 🚀 The Solution
- **Visual Tiles**: Each method/class becomes a clickable tile
- **Natural Instructions**: "The back button functionality isn't working properly"
- **Code Discovery**: Click to reveal/hide implementation details

## ✨ Features
- 📦 **Tile-based Code Visualization**
- 🔍 **Expandable Code Details**
- ✏️ **Direct Edit Requests**
- 🤖 **AI Integration Ready**

## 🎯 Demo
python code_visualizer.py

text

## 🎮 How It Works
1. AI generates code with descriptive comments
2. Code gets automatically divided into tiles
3. Users see "File Reading", "Data Processing" etc.
4. Click tiles to see actual implementation
5. Request modifications in natural language

